text: brasenbae puok anak leatatradeang nouv kar brichcheaktean teang lay ku cheakearola . te brasenbae puok anak leakkambang kar brichcheak ning phdal vea dl anak kreikr noh vea kuchea kar brasaer bamphot samreab puok anak . haey a l laoh nung loubleang babakamm neanea robsa puok anak . haey a l laoh mha doeng nouv avei del puok anak br pru td
